						type: "text",
						content: { body: "\n          <p>\n            Diia is an online platform and app developed by the Ministry of Digital Transformation of Ukraine, offering over 23 million citizens digital access to 33 essential government documents—including ID cards, driver's licenses, and passports—and more than 150 services covering everything from traffic tickets to taxes. The platform’s next phase is an AI-powered transformation: Diia.AI, an agent designed to proactively offer services and eliminate bureaucracy.\n          </p>\n          <p>\n            The team chose Gemini 2.0 Flash to build it due to its superior cost-efficiency and performance, and to host it via Vertex AI for maximum data security.\n          </p>" }
