							body: "\n            <p>\n              Marketers often face a \"blank page problem\" when initiating creator campaigns: identifying suitable creators, defining ad types, and allocating budgets. Passionfroot developed its AI Campaign Strategist to automate this process and help marketers scale their efforts.\n            </p>\n            <p>\n              The AI agent uses Gemini models to generate tailored creator marketing campaigns based on specific audience and growth targets. It provides recommendations on creators, budget allocation, content placements and estimates expected CPM and engagement.\n            </p>\n            <p>\n              Passionfroot needed a model capable of understanding the nuances of effective creator marketing to guide the agent's strategy.\n            </p>"
